	Studies: 
Degree in biology, computer science, computational biology, bioinformatics or biostatistics 
A PhD in computer science, computational biology or bioinformatics is a plus

==========================================
Le paragraphe 9 est en : english
	Technical skills required:
Experience in team management of min. 3 years
Knowledge of Database Programming
Experience in Genome assembly and annotation, NGS and Proteomics analyses 
Experience in Perl or Python, R programming and UNIX 

==========================================
Le paragraphe 10 est en : english
	Additional beneficial skills:
Be service-oriented and motivated to take on the challenge of leading a Core Facility
Ability to provide service to a large, international scientific community
An open personality, and the capability to easily interact with people of different scientific backgrounds, nationalities and personalities
Ability to influence, develop and communicate effectively with the team

==========================================
